' Shared PRINT profile for Letter/PPT exports
' Tuned for legibility when printed on 8.5x11 or pasted into slides.

skinparam dpi 220
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam Padding 10
skinparam nodesep 34
skinparam ranksep 38

' Keep within practical page/slide bounds while preserving readability.
scale max 1050 width
